{"tid":1816934,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無方法搞到班仆街親戚無左層公屋","createTime":"2020-01-08T15:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T17:32:01.000Z","uid":154617,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6c7297fd81082af074aceba535f31dab3cec569a","tid":1816934,"uid":154617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"我識個老人家同佢個仔、新抱、2個孫一齊住公屋<br />\n老人家已經年過90<br />\n半年黎身上成日有傷<br />\n介傷、疼、腫咩都有<br />\n最近仲腦出血入左ICU<br />\n雖然無証據，但懷疑比同住既人打<br />\n疑似想趕走老人家，佔左間公屋<br />\n而家排緊期入老人院<br />\n由於唔算好親，我完全話唔到事<br />\n<br />\n間公屋有晒一家五口個名，老人家係戶主<br />\n如果老人家真係住老人院，間公屋就會比左班仆街<br />\n想問有無方法可以攬炒<br />\n老人家入老人院，公屋寧願比返政府都唔益班仆街"},{"pid":"300b002625d76dceb12b3faab7ada84f4b0133c5","tid":1816934,"uid":93649,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"CCTV"},{"pid":"34c935f617f58661b195db49981d98dd1592169f","tid":1816934,"uid":75924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:58:34.000Z","msg":"搵社工跟進？虐老佢地應該有經驗處理"},{"pid":"dd5c231c112c67a64736376de6cf34a7a5d27ff2","tid":1816934,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:59:53.000Z","msg":"主要都係睇個老人家想點先"},{"pid":"20efcb9bbd111255a541f670ef1d6e36c6752448","tid":1816934,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:00:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n火魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"87cf3a1b65bf56aeb2caee8b0b2f7c4bb0face52","tid":1816934,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"個老人家同你咩關係?<br />\n清官都難審家庭事, 你知條春?"},{"pid":"84f7baa202e3680ad7b8832f60dcf3a327ff289f","tid":1816934,"uid":154617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34c935f617f58661b195db49981d98dd1592169f","tid":1816934,"uid":75924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:58:34.000Z","msg":"搵社工跟進？虐老佢地應該有經驗處理"},"citedBy":